sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Runner
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant Index as models-index.yaml<br/>(Local Files)
    participant RHIO as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as huggingface.co<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RHACCESS as registry.access.redhat.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Output as Catalog Files<br/>(Local)
    participant Konflux as Konflux Pipeline
    participant Quay as quay.io/rhoai<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>(On-Cluster)
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation Pipeline (CI/CD)

    CI->>Index: Read models-index.yaml,<br/>validated-models-index.yaml,<br/>other-models-index.yaml
    CI->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor
    Extractor->>RHIO: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, No Auth
    RHIO-->>Extractor: OCI Manifest (architectures, timestamps)
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>Extractor: Model details, README, collections
    Extractor->>Output: Write per-model metadata<br/>(output/*.yaml)
    Extractor->>Output: Write data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/validated-models-catalog.yaml<br/>data/other-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation (CI/CD)

    CI->>Index: Read *-mcp-servers-index.yaml
    CI->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor (MCP mode)
    Extractor->>RHACCESS: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, No Auth
    RHACCESS-->>Extractor: MCP Server OCI metadata
    Extractor->>Output: Write data/*-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Container Build & Push

    Konflux->>Output: COPY data/ into container image<br/>(Dockerfile.konflux)
    Konflux->>Quay: Push odh-model-metadata-collection<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, Quay credentials

    Note over CI,Dashboard: Flow 3: Runtime Data Consumption (On-Cluster)

    Container->>Container: sleep infinity<br/>(keeps pod alive)
    Dashboard->>Container: Volume mount /app/data<br/>Shared filesystem, Pod-level RBAC
    Dashboard-->>Dashboard: Render model catalog UI
